        paceLabel = "Slow and Steady";
        paceDesc = "You believe great relationships are built one careful step at a time. You prioritize certainty, emotional safety, and deep trust before moving to the next stage. While your pace may test impatient partners, those who stay will experience a profoundly intentional and secure connection.";
